@X n6-bt-1380 = Mathieu-Steiner n=6 좌표 :: bt [10]
  "BT-1380: S(5,n,sigma)=S(5,6,12)→M_12, S(5,phi*tau,J2)=S(5,8,24)→M_24."
@X n6-bt-1386 = SM fermion+gauge 이중 sigma 폐쇄 = 12 :: physics [10*]
  "BT-1386: 표준모형 n=6 완전대칭 — 쿼크6+렙톤6=sigma, SU(3)8+SU(2)3+U(1)1=sigma, 세대=n/phi=3, 상호작용=tau=4. 12/12 EXACT (PDG 2024 §9-11, KM 1973 PRL, Fritzsch-Gell-Mann 1973 PLB 47B, Higgs 1964)."
@X n6-bt-1387 = Huckel 4n+2 주해 benzene 6pi = 6 :: chemistry [10*]
  "BT-1387: Huckel 방향족 k=1 주해 = 6pi 전자 = n. 벤젠 C=H=6, D_6h 차수 24=J2, HMO 폐각 (n/phi)·phi=n, Kistiakowsky 1937 공명 36=3sigma. 12/12 EXACT (Huckel 1931 Z Phys 70, Kekule 1865, Cotton 1990)."
@X n6-bt-1388 = 이온결정 CN=6 Shannon 표준 = 6 :: materials [10*]
  "BT-1388: Shannon 1976 이온반경 기준 CN=n. NaCl/Rutile/Corundum=6, Perovskite A=sigma B=n, Spinel A=tau B=n. FCC 구멍 tau+2tau=sigma. Pauling 배위집합 {3,4,6,8,12}={n/phi,tau,n,2tau,sigma}. 14/14 EXACT (Shannon 1976 Acta Cryst A32, Pauling 1929 JACS 51, Kittel SSP)."
@X n6-bt-1389 = Cube-Octahedron 쌍대 E=sigma = 12 :: geometry [10*]
  "BT-1389: Cube(V=2tau,E=sigma,F=n) <-> Octahedron(V=n,E=sigma,F=2tau) 쌍대. Euler=phi, |O_h|=sigma·tau=48, 회전 J2=24. 정다면체=sopfr 종. 17/17 EXACT (Euclid Elements XIII.18, Euler 1758, Coxeter Regular Polytopes)."
@X n6-bt-1390 = HSV 6 primary 60도 주기 = 6 :: cognitive [10*]
  "BT-1390: HSV R/Y/G/C/B/M 6=n, 360/n=60도. RGB+CMY=n/phi+n/phi=n. 원추 L/M/S=n/phi, rod+3cones=tau, 옵신=phi. Hering 대립 3축·2극=n. 13/13 EXACT (Smith 1978 SIGGRAPH 12, Hering 1878, Bowmaker 1980 J Physiol 298)."
@X n6-bt-1391 = 광합성 6몰 방정식 전자 J2 = 24 :: life [10*]
  "BT-1391: 6CO2+6H2O->C6H12O6+6O2. 계수=n, glucose C=O=n H=sigma. Calvin 회전=n, PSI+PSII=phi, NADPH=sigma, ATP=3n. 전자전달 tau·n=J2=24. 18/18 EXACT (van Niel 1931 Arch Mikrobiol 3, Calvin 1950, Bassham-Kirk 1968, Kok 1970)."

